\begin_layout Standard
设空间闭区域Ω是由分片光滑的闭曲面Σ所围成，函数P(x,y,z)、Q(x,y,z)、R(x,y,z)在Ω上具有一阶连续偏导数，则有 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\iiint\limits _{\Omega}\left(\frac{\partial P}{\partial x}+\frac{\partial Q}{\partial y}+\frac{\partial R}{\partial z}\right)\Diff v=\oiint_{\Sigma}P\,\Diff y\Diff z+Q\,\Diff z\Diff x+R\,\Diff z\Diff y
\]

\end_inset


